title: DDFP 345: Greatest sports theme music tournament
itunes:title: DDFP 345: Greatest sports theme music tournament
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank to shed light on the mystery surrounding the 2nd pick in the 2015 NFL Draft (11:03). Then, Shek and Handsome give their opinion on who holds the title for greatest sports theme music of all time (21:00). 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
